  quest_name: "Don\u2019t Go Empty-Handed"
  description: "You\u2019re new. I can tell. And out there? New gets you killed.\n\nYou\u2019ll
    need a weapon\u2014something that won\u2019t snap in your hands. I had a blade\u2026
    bought it off a strange fella. Half mad, but he knew steel.\n\nLeft it with Joe,
    the blacksmith. Go on\u2014he\u2019s holding onto it. Try not to die before you
    get back."
